#. </strong><span class="gloss">
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc83:28.1"
msgid "yattha katthaci rañño sayanaṃ paññattaṃ hoti, antamaso sāṇipākāraparikkhittampi."
msgstr ""

#. </span>
#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="24"></a>
#. <strong class="term">
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc83:29.1"
msgid "Indakhīlaṃ atikkāmeyyāti"
msgstr ""

#. </strong><span class="gloss">
msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc83:29.1"
msgid "paṭhamaṃ pādaṃ ummāraṃ atikkāmeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""

#. </span>

msgctxt "pi-tv-bu-vb-pc83:29.2"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ pādaṃ atikkāmeti, āpatti pācittiyassa."
msgstr ""

